When `r = 100` and `dx = -100`, are you still going to search `dy` from `-100` to `100`??
Nearly all of solutions are doing
```
for (int dx = -r; dx <= r; dx++)
	for (int dy = -r; dy <= r; dy++) if (dx*dx+dy*dy <= r)
	{ ... }
